&gt;&gt; only for viper modchip &lt;&lt;

&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Now in french too!&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;

i have compiled a mp3player plugin with the cobra bios v1.2.
&gt;&gt; there is now a mp3player in the viper menu.

*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*

you just have to &gt;burn &quot;cobra1.2+mp3playerincluded.vgc&quot; with your mp3 on a disk (file system = iso 9600only , nothing else alowed)
&gt;then , flash your bios
&gt;reboot , and enjoy!!!!

*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
if you dont want to flash your bios , burn your mp3 with the mp3player.dol file
, just launch it from the explorer.
*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
if you want to compile your own bios , the pugin file to add is mp3player.cbp
